    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  HIV positive

          -  Stable antiretroviral regimen for &gt; 3months containing either abacavir or tenofovir

          -  Suppressed HIV viral load

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Current cigarette smoking

          -  Pre-existing platelet disorder

          -  current or recent (last 6 months) antiplatelet therapy

          -  pregnancy
      </textblock>
